---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.png';
import ProfessionalJourney from '../assets/Professional_Journey.png';
import TechnicalCore from '../assets/Technical_Core_Competencies.png';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me: The Architect Behind the AI 🛠️"
	description="Senior Technical Architect specializing in future-proofing legacy environments with AI and enterprise systems."
	pubDate={new Date('April 15 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<style>
		@keyframes pulse {
			0% { transform: scale(1); }
			50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
			100% { transform: scale(1); }
		}
		@keyframes fadeIn {
			from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
			to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
		}
		@keyframes slideInLeft {
			from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50px); }
			to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
		}
		@keyframes bounce {
			0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
			50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
		}
		@keyframes float {
			0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
			50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
		}
		@keyframes glow {
			0%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.5); }
			50% { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 1); }
		}
		@keyframes rotate {
			from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
			to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
		}
		@keyframes shimmer {
			0% { background-position: -1000px 0; }
			100% { background-position: 1000px 0; }
		}
		h2 {
			animation: slideInLeft 1s ease-out;
		}
		p, ul, img {
			animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
		}
		hr {
			animation: fadeIn 2s ease-out;
		}
	</style>
	<p style="animation: bounce 2s infinite;">
		Hello! I'm Vinayak Manjare, a Senior Technical Architect 🎯 based in Pune. With over 15 years of experience, I've built the backbone of high-stakes enterprise systems across BFSI, Procurement, and E-commerce. I specialize in "future-proofing" legacy environments. Lately, that means bridging the gap between experimental LLMs and production-grade software.  I don't just build AI; I build the architectural plumbing that makes it reliable, secure, and cost-effective. 🚀
	</p>

	<h2><img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/briefcase.png" alt="Journey" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px; animation: rotate 3s linear infinite;" /> My Professional Journey 📈</h2>
	<img src={ProfessionalJourney.src} alt="Professional Journey" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;" />
	<p>
		From mastering product foundations at Yardi to engineering real-time data streaming for Deutsche Bank, I've focused on systems that stay live 99.9% ⏱️ of the time.
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Product Foundation (2011–2018):</strong> Spent 7 years at Yardi, leading the internationalization of the US platform for the UK market.</li>
		<li><strong>Enterprise Scale (2018–2022):</strong> Engineered identity platforms for Charles Schwab and high-velocity monitoring for Deutsche Bank.</li>
		<li><strong>AI Innovation (2023–Present):</strong> Currently a Project Lead at Persistent, transforming legacy sourcing platforms into AI-enabled powerhouses.</li>
	</ul>

	<hr />

	<h2><img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/brain.png" alt="Brain" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" /> 🧠 Technical Core & Impact ⚡</h2>
	<img src={TechnicalCore.src} alt="Technical Core Competencies" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;" />
	<p>
		I focus on technology that is fiscally responsible. Recently, I reduced AWS Fargate monthly costs by 25% through strategic microservices refactoring. <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/money.png" alt="Money" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 8px;" /><br />
		<img src="https://quickchart.io/chart?c={type:'bar',data:{labels:['Before','After'],datasets:[{label:'Monthly Cost (USD)',data:[4000,3000],backgroundColor:['#FF6B6B','#51CF66']}]},options:{plugins:{legend:{display:false}},scales:{y:{beginAtZero:true}}}}" alt="Cost Reduction Graph - 25% Savings" width="350" style="display: block; margin: 10px 0; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;" />
		The AI Edge: RAG Pipeline Design, Prompt Engineering, and custom metadata caching that slashed token costs by 60% 💰. <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/artificial-intelligence.png" alt="AI" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 8px;" /> Modern Backend: Java 17, Spring Boot 3.2, and Microservices consolidation. Data & Cloud: AWS Specialist (Lambda, Fargate, S3) and Confluent Certified Data Streaming Engineer.
	</p>

	<hr />

	<h2><img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/trophy.png" alt="Trophy" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px; animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;" /> 🏆 Verified Certifications ✨</h2>
	<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
		<a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/4d4693bb-530e-4bca-9327-de07f3aa2348">
			<img src="https://images.credly.com/images/4d4693bb-530e-4bca-9327-de07f3aa2348/image.png" width="80" alt="AWS Certified AI Practitioner" style="margin-right: 10px; animation: pulse 2s infinite;" />
		</a>
		<div style="animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite;">
			<strong>AWS Certified AI Practitioner</strong><br />
			Focuses on implementing AI/ML solutions on AWS, including generative AI foundation models and responsible AI.
		</div>
	</div>
	<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
		<a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/4136ced8-75d5-4afb-8677-40b6236e2672">
			<img src="https://images.credly.com/images/4136ced8-75d5-4afb-8677-40b6236e2672/azure-ai-fundamentals-600x600.png" width="80" alt="Microsoft Certified: Azure AI Fundamentals (AI-900)" style="margin-right: 10px; animation: pulse 2s infinite;" />
		</a>
		<div style="animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite;">
			<strong>Microsoft Certified: Azure AI Fundamentals (AI-900)</strong><br />
			Demonstrates foundational knowledge of AI and ML workloads on Microsoft Azure.
		</div>
	</div>

	<hr />

	<h2><img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/handshake.png" alt="Connect" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px; animation: float 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;" /> 🤝 Let's Connect 🌐</h2>
	<p style="animation: float 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;">
		<img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/marker.png" alt="Location" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" /> <strong>Location</strong>: Pune, Maharashtra 🇮🇳<br />
		<img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/24/000000/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" /> <strong>LinkedIn</strong>: <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/vinayakmanjare">linkedin.com/in/vinayakmanjare</a>
	</p>
</Layout>